media:group.media:title: Past Tense in Finnish
media:group.media:description:
Past Tense In Finnish,
Miten suomeksi puhutaan menneisyydestä? 
Now we can learn something new - how to talk about the past in Finnish!learn a simple way, on how to change present to past tense. An easy and fast way to learn and develop your Finnish language skills.
